                            <comment id="17004516" author="daniel_sun" created="Sat, 28 Dec 2019 16:30:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Could you try the code with the latest version of groovy 3.0.0? I find it works with groovy-3.0.0-rc-2:&lt;/p&gt;

