===&amp;gt; 1.0
groovy:000&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17004518" author="daniel_sun" created="Sat, 28 Dec 2019 16:32:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/groovy/blob/master/src/test/groovy/bugs/Groovy8948.groovy&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/groovy/blob/master/src/test/groovy/bugs/Groovy8948.groovy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17006386" author="nmccloud" created="Wed, 1 Jan 2020 11:51:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It actually works dynamically; however, if you compile statically it will not.&#160; Sorry for not mentioning that earlier.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;Foo {
&#160; &#160; void foo() {
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Math&lt;/span&gt;.ceil(1/2);
&#160; &#160; }
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When running &lt;b&gt;groovyc --compile-static&lt;/b&gt; on it, it fails:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Foo.groovy: 3: [Static type checking] - Cannot find matching method java.lang.Math#ceil(java.math.BigDecimal). Please check if the declared type is correct and if the method exists.
 @ line 3, column 9.
         Math.ceil(1/2);
         ^
1 error
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
